"biblScope\">1.141</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τοῖο δ᾽ ἅμα ψυχήν τε καὶ ἔγχεος ἐξέρυσ᾽ αἰχμήν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:505\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.505</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">snatch out of,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐξείρυσε χειρὸς τόξον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:870\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.870</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸν . . λαβὼν ποδὸς ἐξερύσασκε</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by</tr_> the foot, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:490\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.490</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">draw out,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τοὺς δ᾽ ἐξείρυσσαν Ἀχαιοί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:194\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.194</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tear out,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μήδεά τ᾽ ἐξερύσας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:87\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.87</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν γλῶσσαν ἐξειρύσας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.38